2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jf86-639r-gxrp/GHSA-jf86-639r-gxrp.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0285.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82091/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0475.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0462","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0462.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0276","title":"Hughes Technologies mSQL 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"mSQL（Mini SQL）2.0.1 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标服务的 1114 端口发送特制的畸型数据包，触发栈缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖返回地址，实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 mSQL 2.0.1 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0276"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.350","remediation":"立即将 mSQL 升级至 v2.0.1 以上版本（如 2.0.2 或更高），该版本修复了 wprint 函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。由于 mSQL 已停止维护多年，强烈建议迁移至受支持的数据库产品，如 MariaDB 或 PostgreSQL。在无法迁移前，应通过在防火墙上限制对 mSQL 默认端口（1114/TCP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 IP 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0276","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0276.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0276","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0276.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0276.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0276.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j548-f7g3-8wxc/GHSA-j548-f7g3-8wxc.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.863","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0276.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0462.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0454","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0454.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0268","title":"MetaInfo MetaWeb 文件上传与脚本执行漏洞","description":"MetaInfo MetaWeb Web 服务器存在未授权脚本上传与执行漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求向目标服务器上传任意脚本文件，并直接访问执行该脚本，从而获取服务器控制权或执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 MetaWeb 多个版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前厂商已停止维护，建议用户迁移至其他 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0268"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.347","remediation":"立即停止使用 MetaInfo MetaWeb 服务器，该产品已停止维护且无安全更新可用。迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx），并配置严格的上传权限控制，禁止脚本文件在可写目录下执行。如无法立即迁移，应将服务器置于隔离网络并限制外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/110","http://www.osvdb.org/3969","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19084","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0268.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelis