roject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0255","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0255.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3phx-q7wc-mf8g/GHSA-3phx-q7wc-mf8g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0ec05ae5-953f-4811-908d-245d2cf1e5af.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0440.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0433","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0433.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0248","title":"SSH sshd 认证代理竞争条件漏洞","description":"SSH 服务软件 sshd 1.2.17 版本的身份认证代理机制存在竞争条件漏洞（Race Condition）。远程攻击者在认证窗口内利用时序差向目标发送精心构造的认证请求，可在合法用户完成认证前截获或替换其身份凭证，从而窃取其他用户的 SSH 登录凭据并获得未授权访问。该漏洞影响早期 SSH 协议实现，利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露和系统被控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0248"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.860","remediation":"升级至 sshd 1.2.18 及以上版本，该版本已修复认证代理机制中的条件竞争漏洞。也可迁移至 OpenSSH（自 1999 年起开源维护），并保持版本更新。若无法升级，限制对 ssh-agent 的本地访问权限，仅允许受信任用户使用代理转发功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/mUNIXes/ssh2.html","http://www.uni-karlsruhe.de/~ig25/ssh-faq/ssh-faq-6.html#ss6.1","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0248.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0248","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0248.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcr-j22h-735c/GHSA-vhcr-j22h-735c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82092/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0248.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0433.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0428","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0243","title":"Linux cfingerd 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux cfingerd（可配置的 Finger 服务守护进程）存在远程权限提升漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 Finger 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取目标系统 root 最高权限，完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版中运行的 cfingerd 服务，攻击者无需任何认证即可远程发起攻击，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0243"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.250","remediation":"立即停止并卸载 cfingerd 服务（`systemctl stop cfingerd && apt-get remove cfingerd` 或 `yum remove cfingerd`）。cfingerd 已在 2000 年代初停止维护，不存在补丁修复。建议在 iptables 或防火墙中封禁 TCP 端口 79，同时禁用 finger 协议。改用现代认证机制（如 LDAP/SSSD）替代 finger 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.geocrawler.com/archives/3/92/1996/9/0/2217716/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0243","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0243.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_format_bug.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80889/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0243.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0425","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0240","title":"防火墙或过滤器 IP分片SYN数据包 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"部分防火墙或网络过滤器在处理分片 SYN 数据包时存在策略绕过漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送设置了 IP 保留位的特制分片 SYN 数据包，绕过防火墙或过滤器的访问控制规则，未经授权访问受保护的内部网络资源。该漏洞影响多种品牌和型号的防火墙产品，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商通过更新防火墙的分片重组和标志位检查逻辑修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0240"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.897","remediation":"对防火墙启用状态检测（Stateful Inspection）功能，确保所有IP分片报文在重组完成后再进行规则匹配，禁止直接放行分片SYN包。同时在防火墙上配置策略丢弃IP头部保留位非零的数据包，并禁用非必要接口的IP路由转发功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0240.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0416","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0416.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0231","title":"IP-Switch IMail 和 Seattle Labs Slmail 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IP-Switch IMail 与 Seattle Labs Slmail 2.6 邮件服务软件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 SMTP 服务发送超长 VRFY 命令参数触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝服务，在特定条件下可进一步实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响上述邮件系统的 SMTP 组件，利用无需认证，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0231"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.770","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 SLMail 2.6 及更早版本的 VRFY 命令处理中，超长参数导致栈缓冲区溢出。厂商后续版本已修复此问题，建议尽快升级至 SLMail 3.0 及以上版本，或迁移至 Ipswitch IMail 最新版本。若无法立即升级，应在 SMTP 代理或 IPS 设备上限制 VRFY 命令参数长度不超过 256 字节，并禁用 VRFY/EXPN 命令以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/slmail.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80916/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0416.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0410","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0410.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0220","title":"IRC Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IRC 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 IRC 服务器发送特制数据包，导致服务器进程崩溃，使其无法为正常用户提供聊天服务。该漏洞影响多种 IRC 服务器软件，攻击者仅需具备网络访问能力即可触发，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0220"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.423","remediation":"升级 ircd 至 2.10.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复因畸形数据包导致的服务器崩溃问题。对于无法升级的旧系统，可在 IRC 服务前端部署 TCP 代理或应用层防火墙，过滤异常连接请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0220","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0220.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0220","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rhw-5hch-3fh6/GHSA-9rhw-5hch-3fh6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80885/info.html","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0220.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0410.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0390","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0390.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0205","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.6.11/8.6.12 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.6.11 及 8.6.12 版本存在拒绝服务漏洞。作为广泛使用的邮件传输代理（MTA），Sendmail 在处理特制的网络请求时存在缺陷，未经认证的远程攻击者可利用此漏洞向目标服务器发送恶意构造的数据包，导致 Sendmail 服务进程崩溃或停止响应，从而造成邮件服务中断。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需任何身份认证即可远程触发，影响系统可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0205"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.477","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.6.13 或更高版本，该版本已修复此拒绝服务漏洞。若无法立即升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制连接速率和最大并发连接数，并在网络边界启用流量过滤以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0390.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0383","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0383.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0200","title":"Microsoft Windows NT FTP Server 未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT FTP 服务器（WFTP）在默认配置中启用了无密码的 guest 账户，远程攻击者可利用任意用户名和密码成功登录 FTP 服务器，获取未经授权的文件访问权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用，对系统的机密性构成严重威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0200"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.867","remediation":"立即禁用 Windows NT 的 Guest 帐户（或为其设置强密码），并配置 FTP 服务禁止匿名/来宾登录。在 FTP 服务器上设置用户权限最小化，限制可访问目录。建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 2016/2019/2022），因 Windows NT 已停止安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=137853"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0383.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0382","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0382.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0198","title":"多个Unix系统 finger服务 远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Finger 服务（TCP 79 端口）存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标发送 finger 查询请求（如 finger .@host），获取系统上的用户账户列表及登录状态。该漏洞源于 Finger 协议默认未对查询请求做访问控制，导致攻击者可借此收集有效用户名，为进一步的暴力破解或社会工程学攻击提供基础。影响运行 Finger 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0198"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.610","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务：在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释或删除 finger 行并重启服务（`kill -HUP <inetd_pid>`），或执行 `systemctl disable finger`（现代系统）。同时使用防火墙阻断外部对 tcp/79 端口的访问。如确需使用，改用 cfingerd 并限制输出信息量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/8378"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0382.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0380","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0380.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0197","title":"多种Unix操作系统 Finger 远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Finger 服务（TCP 79 端口）存在用户信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何认证，通过发送 `finger 0@host` 查询即可获取目标系统上的用户账户信息，包括用户名、真实姓名、终端状态、最后登录时间等敏感数据。攻击者可利用这些信息进行账户枚举，为后续的暴力破解或社会工程学攻击奠定基础。该漏洞影响运行 Finger 服务的各类 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0197"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.497","remediation":"立即在系统层面禁用 finger 服务：Systemd 系统执行 `systemctl stop finger && systemctl disable finger`，SysVinit 系统执行 `service finger stop && chkconfig finger off`。同时在防火墙（iptables/nftables）阻止入站连接端口 79/tcp。如确需远程查询功能，替换为受限版本如 `finge-rus` 并限制查询来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/8378"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0380.toml"}]